Package: logthis
Title: Structured Logging Framework for R
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Siqi",
           family = "Zhang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "iqis.gnahz@gmail.com")
Author: Siqi Zhang [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Siqi Zhang <iqis.gnahz@gmail.com>
Description: A flexible, structured logging framework for R applications.
    Provides hierarchical event levels, multiple output receivers (console, files,
    cloud storage), configurable filtering, and rich metadata support. Designed
    for R packages, data analysis pipelines, Shiny applications, and pharmaceutical
    GxP compliance (21 CFR Part 11, ALCOA+). Integrates with validation frameworks
    (validate, pointblank, arsenal) for complete audit trails. For Shiny integration,
    see the 'logshiny' package.
